prediction.sparql:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?series ( COUNT( ?episode ) AS ?episodeCount ) ?numVotes WHERE {
  ?series rdf:type imdb:Movie .
  ?series imdb:numVotes ?numVotes .
  FILTER ( ?numVotes > 1000000 ) .
  ?episode imdb:parentTitle ?series .
}
GROUP BY ?series ?numVotes
ORDER BY DESC ( ?episodeCount )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?genre ( COUNT( ?title ) AS ?frequency ) ( AVG( ?rating ) AS ?averageRating ) WHERE {
  ?title imdb:genre ?genre .
  ?title imdb:averageRating ?rating .
}
GROUP BY ?genre
ORDER BY DESC ( ?frequency )

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?person ?personLabel ( COUNT( ?movie ) AS ?movieCount ) WHERE {
  ?person imdb:knownForTitle ?movie .
  ?movie imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  FILTER ( ?votes > 1000000 ) .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel
  }
}
GROUP BY ?person ?personLabel
HAVING ( COUNT( ?movie ) >= 3 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?movieCount )
LIMIT 20

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?series ?seriesLabel ( AVG( ?rating ) AS ?avgRating ) ( COUNT( ?episode ) AS ?episodeCount ) WHERE {
  ?series imdb:titleType "tvSeries" .
  ?series rdfs:label ?seriesLabel .
  ?episode imdb:titleType "tvEpisode" .
  ?episode imdb:parentTitle ?series .
  ?episode imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  ?episode imdb:averageRating ?rating .
  FILTER ( ?votes >= 10000 )
}
GROUP BY ?series ?seriesLabel
HAVING ( COUNT( ?episode ) >= 20 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?avgRating )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX imdb_principal: <https://www.imdb.com/principal/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?titleActor ?titleDirector WHERE {
  ?titleActor imdb:numVotes ?votesActor .
  FILTER ( ?votesActor > 100000 ) .
  ?titleDirector imdb:numVotes ?votesDirector .
  FILTER ( ?votesDirector > 100000 ) .
  ?titleActor imdb_principal:actor ?person .
  ?titleDirector imdb_principal:director ?person .
  FILTER ( ?titleActor != ?titleDirector ) .
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  ?actor imdb:knownForTitle ?title1 .
  ?title1 imdb:isAdult true .
  ?actor imdb:knownForTitle ?title2 .
  ?title2 imdb:isAdult false .
  ?title2 imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  FILTER ( ?votes >= 100000 ) .
}
GROUP BY ?actor
HAVING ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?title1 ) >= 3 && COUNT( DISTINCT ?title2 ) >= 1 )

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX imdb_principal: <https://www.imdb.com/principal/>
SELECT ?director ?directorName ?movie ?movieTitle ?rating ?votes WHERE {
  ?movie imdb:titleType "movie" .
  ?movie imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  FILTER ( ?votes >= 100000 ) .
  ?movie imdb:averageRating ?rating .
  ?movie imdb_principal:director ?director .
  ?director rdfs:label ?directorName .
  ?movie rdfs:label ?movieTitle .
  {
    SELECT ?director ( MAX( ?ratingSub ) AS ?maxRating ) WHERE {
      ?movieSub imdb:titleType "movie" .
      ?movieSub imdb:numVotes ?votesSub .
      FILTER ( ?votesSub >= 100000 ) .
      ?movieSub imdb:averageRating ?ratingSub .
      ?movieSub imdb_principal:director ?director .
    }
    GROUP BY ?director
  }
  FILTER ( ?rating = ?maxRating )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?rating )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX imdb_principal: <https://www.imdb.com/principal/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor ?actorBirthYear ?movie ?movieStartYear ( ?movieStartYear - ?actorBirthYear AS ?ageAtRelease ) WHERE {
  ?movie imdb:titleType "movie" .
  ?movie imdb:numVotes ?numVotes .
  FILTER ( ?numVotes >= 100000 ) .
  ?movie imdb_principal:actor ?actor .
  ?actor imdb:birthYear ?actorBirthYear .
  ?movie imdb:startYear ?movieStartYear .
  FILTER ( ?actorBirthYear <= ?movieStartYear ) .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?ageAtRelease )
LIMIT 100

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX imdb_principal: <https://www.imdb.com/principal/>
SELECT ?actor ?director ( COUNT( ?movie ) AS ?collaborations ) WHERE {
  ?movie imdb_principal:actor ?actor ; imdb:director ?director ; imdb:numVotes ?votes ; imdb:titleType "movie" .
  FILTER ( ?votes >= 100000 )
}
GROUP BY ?actor ?director
HAVING ( COUNT( ?movie ) >= 5 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?collaborations )
LIMIT 10
